	(2240, 20427, 'EN', 1, '<p><strong>Other Strategic Objectives:</strong></p><p>To reduce the number of work accidents by 20 per cent in the next 10 years&nbsp;</p><p>To ensure the safe use of hazardous chemical substances in work processes and to replace hazardous chemicals with less hazardous ones</p><p>Implementing, monitoring and upgrading programmes promoting physical and mental health in the workplace directed at preventing chronic diseases and maintaining the ability to work</p><p>Ensuring high-quality implementation of expert tasks by occupational health providers</p>');
